init_text: All of the "#1 Dad" mugs in the world change to show the actual ranking of Dads suddenly.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The government promised to investigate and fix the problem.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: that there was one man, a doctor named Bob McHenry who accidentally sent out a pulse from his lab that altered all of the DNA in the world

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Bob agreed to work with the government and try to fix this problem.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: he was right and all the mugs were fixed, which is why we can now see Dad as rank #1 again.
